Package org.drip.measure.continuous

Class R1UnivariateExponential

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.measure.continuous.R1Univariate
      • org.drip.measure.continuous.R1UnivariateExponential
  • public class R1UnivariateExponential
extends R1Univariate
    R1UnivariateExponential implements the Univariate R1 Exponential Distribution. It implements the Incremental, the Cumulative, and the Inverse Cumulative Distribution Densities.

    • Module = Numerical Core Module
    • Library = Numerical Optimizer Library
    • Project = Measure
    • Package = Continuous
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
